parameters.name: endTime
parameters.description: The end of the time range to query. The value must be a UNIX timestamp.

parameters.name: page
parameters.description: The number of the page to return. Valid values: 1 to 200. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: size
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Valid values: 1 to 500. Default value: 10.

parameters.name: startTime
parameters.description: The beginning of the time range to query. The value must be a UNIX timestamp.

parameters.name: trigger
parameters.description: The method that is used to trigger health diagnostics. Valid values: SYSTEM, INNER, and USER.
